{"id":393074,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/63/09/630985.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"番組WIKI計画","groupHref":"/group/wiki","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/01/128.jpg","message":"BGM收录范围里是这么写的：<div class=\"quote\"><q>   1.3.3 音乐<br>　　• 曲目相同，封面不同的各种初回版，限定版只收录一份。<br>　　• 不同曲目的各种初回版可以收录，并关联为不同版本。</q></div><span style=\"font-size:20px; line-height:20px;\">疑问：<br>1.以下这些情况哪些可以拆分为多个条目？</span><br><br>1-1.<a href=\"https://chii.in/subject/297146\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Disco Elysium Soundtrack》</a>的加强版：<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">《Disco Elysium - The Final Cut Soundtrack》</span>新增2首曲目：<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">29 Advesperascit</span>和<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">30 Ignus Nilsen Waltz</span><br><br>1-2.<a href=\"https://chii.in/subject/91295\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Icewind Dale The Soundtrack》</a>的加强版：<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/467600/Icewind_Dale_Enhanced_Edition_Official_Soundtrack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Icewind Dale: Enhanced Edition Official Soundtrack》</a>新增1张碟片含18首新曲、且对应的游戏条目是<a href=\"https://chii.in/subject/256941\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Icewind Dale: Enhanced Edition》</a><br><br>1-3.<a href=\"https://chii.in/subject/215224\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Planescape Torment the Soundtrack》</a>的加强版：<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/613230/Planescape_Torment_Enhanced_Edition_Official_Soundtrack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Planescape: Torment: Enhanced Edition Official Soundtrack》</a>少一首曲子、且对应的游戏条目是<a href=\"https://chii.in/subject/218786\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Planescape: Torment Enhanced Edition》</a><br><br>1-4.<a href=\"https://vgmdb.net/album/41744\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Baldur's Gate II Soundtrack》</a>的加强版：<a href=\"https://chii.in/subject/478195\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Baldur's Gate II: Enhanced Edition Official Soundtrack》</a>新增2张碟片（2~3为新增碟片）和49首曲目（34~82为新增曲目）、且对应的游戏条目是<a href=\"https://chii.in/subject/88428\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Baldur's Gate II: Enhanced Edition》</a><br><br>1-5.《POSTAL: Brain Damaged - Official Soundtrack》的<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/2007440/POSTAL_Brain_Damaged__Official_Soundtrack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">Steam版</a>和<a href=\"https://www.gog.com/game/postal_brain_damaged_official_soundtrack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">GOG版</a>：各自拥有对方没有的曲目，且曲目编号、时长、数量各不相同<br><br>1-6.<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/2142000/Relayer_Advanced_Original_Sound_Track_Into_the_Lost_Code/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Relayer Advanced Original Sound Track -Into the Lost Code-》</a>的加强版：<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/2311700/Relayer_Advanced_Original_Soundtrack_Album_Perfect/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">《Relayer Advanced Original Soundtrack Album Perfect》</a>新增18首曲目（16~33为新增曲目）、且在Steam上分开发售<br><br><br><span style=\"font-size:20px; line-height:20px;\">2.说是要关联为不同版本，可是查看了音乐条目的关联选项列表并没有看到叫做“不同版本”的关联选项，如何关联为不同版本？</span><br><br><a href=\"/user/sai\" class=\"l\">@Sai&#x1F596;</a>","time":"2024-1-29 12:27","title":"音乐专辑的不同版本如何处理？","userId":"druglich","userName":"Druglich","userSign":"(鱼肉行者)"}